headline: Reba Rides Again: Realtor.com® Delivers More Laughs, Listings, and Pet-Friendly Properties in Nearly Home™ New Creative Push
summary: Following the exceptional response to its Nearly HomeTM campaign featuring country icon and sitcom favorite Reba McEntire, today, Realtor.com® is unveiling the next chapter with a fresh set of creative that brings even more real-life real estate challenges to life with humor, heart, and practical solutions.
